divs: Sighting DetailsI was looking out the window waiting for my fiance's papaw to come home, so I can hush the dog when he drives up so my fiance would not wake up. Then I spoted a close plane and watched it for a minute or two then a big gust of wind hit the house because it was windy, then after the wind stoped I saw a disk shaped light dart away really fast, but it was slower and bigger than a comment and really low. and when it took off it left a light streak behind it for a second then it sucked into the path it shot off too
Summary: A light disk takes off at light speed
